column1:
Art,"2011-12-26T21:22:22.45Z","Great Vintage Set","

Great set that I bought when I was a kid.
column2: My box differs a bit from most of the reviews that are elsewhere on the net.&nbsp
column3: According to my box, there are 91 pieces as compared to 86.&nbsp
column4: As well my particular set was manufactured in Stratford Ontario at the Samsonite factory.&nbsp

column1: In any case I remember years of fun after getting this set via mail order and have since watched my family enjoy it as well.
